name: Zooplankton data for Danish marine monitoring (ODAM) from 1991 - 2011
description: Data is an assembly of plankton monitoringstations situated between54Â° and 58Â° North alongthe Danish coasts and in estuaries.There are 6 zooplankton stations that are visited 6 times peryear. Samples are analyzed toestimate zooplankton composition and abundance. The individuals are eithersized or staged andspecies is determined to lowestpossible taxonomical level. This dataset includes multicellular prokaryotes as well as ciliates and same heterotrophicdinoflagellates
